            <p>As a sales engineer, you will work with customers to identify key opportunities for our platform to enhance their data journey.  In this capacity, you’ll be challenged to get involved with engineers and our chief data scientist and grow your understanding of both the state of the art in ML and AI, as well as current themes emerging in the academic literature.</p>

            <p>You are passionate about client-centric solutions and proactively acquiring new enterprise accounts and converting them into long-term clients. You possess a keen ability for overcoming technical obstacles to cost-effectively meet the clients needs today and in the future. You are a hunter. You are intrinsically motivated (... and by financial commissions!). You are a closer. You can demonstrate a history of quota achievement, breaking accounts, overall sales success. You bring a relevant network of strong relationships that are ready to work with you at Data Skeptic.</p>

            <p>You will be responsible for identifying and closing strategic engagements that boost top-line revenue, define, prioritize, chase and close high-growth, high-revenue opportunities.  This is a hands-on sales role best suited for a professional with a strong vision for how artificial intelligence can successfully be brought to market.</p>

            <h2>What we are looking for</h2>
            <ul>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 triangles"><li>Previous enterprise sales experience, ideally with a SaaS and/or ML solution</li></div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 triangles"><li>A track record of efficient use of CRM tools and metric-driven performance.</li></div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 triangles"><li>A high level understanding of concepts like cloud computing, deep learning, and serverless architecture.</li></div>
                </div>
            </ul>

            <h2>Responsibilities</h2>
            <ul>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 triangles">
                        <li>Establish, prospect, develop, build and test into new market segments, converting new</li> customers and prospective customers into a continuous lead pipeline 
