                        <li>Develop strong relationships with customers to create specific repeat business</li>
                        <li>Collaborates with the internal team in the resolution of day-to-day customer and</li> operational issues.
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 triangles">
                        <li>Follow up on inbound sales prospects brought by founder</li>
                        <li>Maintain a healthy deal flow to drive revenue and profitability</li>
                        <li>Track opportunities in a CRM</li>
                        <li>Lead contract scope, terms and pricing negotiations while getting internal alignment on</li> scope and costs
